list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Added new classes and traits in the 'parametric' package
This commit introduces new class and trait definitions in the `parametric` package. The main changes include the addition of the `Option`, `Some`, `None`, `Tree`, `InnerNode`, `Leaf`, `Comparable`, and `Foo` classes and traits. These changes extend the functionality and structure of the project's Scala files. Changes were also made to the `Cell` class and the project workspace configurations were updated.

task.summary:
Added new files and configurations for Scala project
Created several new files and configurations, including Git ignore file, sbt configuration files, IntelliJ IDEA settings files, new Scala class A, and build properties. Also set up the Scala version used in the project to 1.10.0.

Updated workspace configurations and added new Scala files
The commit includes updates to IntelliJ IDEA project configuration files (.idea/workspace.xml, .idea/sbt.xml, etc.) as well as file additions pertaining to Scala classes and traits related to the 'adhoc' and 'parametric' packages. Main features of this commit involve the introduction of class and object definitions in new Scala source files, changes in Scala sbt settings, and the addition of new Git settings and tasks.
